const styles = {
    container: { display: "flex", minHeight: "100vh", width: "100vw", backgroundColor: "#e0f7fa" },
    sidebar: { width: "250px", background: "#add8e6", padding: "20px", boxSizing: "border-box" },
    logo: { width: "80px", height: "80px", marginBottom: "10px", display: "block" },
    sidebarTitle: { fontSize: "20px", color: "#fff", marginBottom: "10px" },
    list: { listStyle: "none", padding: 0, marginBottom: "20px" },
    listItem: { padding: "8px", cursor: "pointer", borderBottom: "1px solid #fff", color: "#000" },
    listItemActive: { padding: "8px", cursor: "pointer", backgroundColor: "#007bff", color: "#fff" },
    newButton: { width: "100%", padding: "8px 12px", backgroundColor: "#007bff", color: "#fff", borderRadius: "4px" },
    main: { flex: 1, padding: "20px", boxSizing: "border-box" },
    title: { fontSize: "26px", marginTop: 0, marginBottom: "20px" },
    input: { width: "100%", padding: "6px", fontSize: "14px", boxSizing: "border-box" },
  };
  
  export default styles;
